{"tid":2015964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（工會戰線手足注意）逾兩成新工會地址唔對辨","createTime":"2020-05-14T05:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T09:47:43.000Z","uid":35814,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f084dd3b049e6ce1a07ae28ea5c1c9524f032c3a","tid":2015964,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:06:10.000Z","msg":"工會戰線嘅彈藥？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://l.hkott.hk/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=25305&amp;ct=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fl.hkott.hk%2Fzh-hk%2Fl%2Fopen-content%3Fcid%3D25305%26ct%3D1&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=831e2cf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://l.hkott.hk/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=25305&amp;ct=1</a><br />\n<br />\n【有線新聞】過去一年湧現大量新工會，由去年6月反修例事件到今個月初，勞工處登記了230個，我們走訪了其中159個，發現有地址人去樓空，有租客不知道公司地址給人用來登記了做工會。<br />\n反修例示威激發黃藍陣營的工會組織潮，由去年6月至今年5月2日，職工會登記局登記了230個新工會，比前年同期大增16倍。當中以工程及建造相關的工會最多，有62個，其次是金融地產及交通運輸。另外登記局還有4092宗申請處理中，這些新工會究竟如何運作？<br />\n<br />\n其他入link睇，太長"},{"pid":"21e2877f3534f3e5070067937cf3abd726ad9206","tid":2015964,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:06:34.000Z","msg":"推比工會戰線手足"},{"pid":"29450f88c814b393fac76186c2b5175c8dfa1b36","tid":2015964,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:07:17.000Z","msg":"做野先<br />\n一陣出街再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff067766baaa1bff37aa510078c73638027f442","tid":2015964,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:13:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23c8d6f7b2445c77499656192eb51c968aebd08f","tid":2015964,"uid":1654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:18:55.000Z","msg":"姐係種票？"},{"pid":"9c95e2c1941bf4e046e378ebbf300578f74a041a","tid":2015964,"uid":91771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:25:42.000Z","msg":"黃嘅就無限期拖<br />\n藍嘅就特快批核"},{"pid":"40bdee751acf7e4221cfcf69898b3d8e896927a8","tid":